Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.84,0:00:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the truth. Is it? My god, it's\Nthe truth. I know cuz I lived it and
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.23,0:00:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,agonized over it and discovered it in my\Nown unconscious and had to undo it and
